description: The attack happened in the early hours of Saturday in West Street in the city centre.
title: Brighton stabbing sees two injured and three arrested
title_page: Brighton stabbing sees two injured and three arrested - BBC News
maintext:
Two men have been taken to hospital after a stabbing in central Brighton.
Sussex Police said one of the men, a 20-year-old, had suffered a stab wound, while an 18-year-old was also injured.
The attacks happened in West Street, near the junction with Middle Street, at about 03.20 GMT.
Three men have been arrested and remain in police custody.
